These are Puzzles for 2x4 Level 6

.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-6-1::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: soy-milk, almond-milk, fanta, hot-chocolate
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: skiing, rowing, snowboarding, climbing
1. the person who's sport is skiing is somewhere to the left of the person who's sport is snowboarding##5
2. the person drinking almond-milk is not the person who's sport is skiing##6
3. the person who's sport is skiing is on the right of the person who's sport is climbing##1
4. the person drinking fanta is on the right of the person who's sport is snowboarding##1
5. the person drinking soy-milk is on the right of the person who's sport is skiing##1
6. the person who's sport is skiing is not the person drinking fanta##6

.:: Answer ::.
|            |     1      |    2     |    3     |    4    |
| Beverage   | almond-milk   | hot-chocolate    | soy-milk    | fanta |
| Sport      | climbing | skiing | snowboarding | rowing |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-6-2::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: almond-milk, tea, water, fanta
There 4 different types of food: tomato, apple, mango, lime
1. the person eating tomato is on the far right##1
2. the person drinking tea is somewhere to the left of the person drinking water##5
3. the person eating lime is somewhere to the left of the person drinking fanta##5
4. the person drinking tea is not the person eating apple##6
5. the person eating lime is on the left of the person drinking water##1
6. the person eating tomato is on the right of the person eating mango##1
7. the person drinking fanta is on the right of the person drinking almond-milk##1
8. the person drinking water is somewhere to the left of the person drinking almond-milk##5

.:: Answer ::.
|            |   1   |     2      |    3     |     4     |
| Beverage   | tea  | water    | almond-milk | fanta    |
| Food       | lime | apple | mango  | tomato |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-6-3::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: juice, mirinda, milk, cola
The people have 4 different jobs:  project-manager, fisherman, security-guard, social-worker
1. the person drinking cola is not the project-manager##6
2. the fisherman is not the person drinking milk##6
3. the security-guard is on the left or right of the person drinking mirinda##3
4. the fisherman is the person drinking juice##1
5. the person drinking mirinda is on the left of the fisherman##1
6. the person drinking juice is in an odd position##4
7. the project-manager is on the far left or far right##3
8. the security-guard is somewhere to the left of the social-worker##5

.:: Answer ::.
|            |      1      |       2        |   3    |   4    |
| Beverage   | cola       | mirinda  | juice  | milk |
| Job        | security-guard | social-worker | fisherman | project-manager  |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-6-4::.
4 different pets are kept: rabbit, ferret, rat, lizard
The people use 4 different means of transport: van, helicopter, scooter, jet-ski
1. the owner of the rat is on the left of the owner of the lizard##1
2. the owner of the ferret is somewhere to the left of the person driving the van##5
3. the person driving the jet-ski is not the owner of the ferret##6
4. the person driving the jet-ski is somewhere to the right of the person driving the van##5
5. the person driving the scooter is on the right of the person driving the helicopter##1
6. the owner of the lizard is somewhere to the left of the person driving the jet-ski##5

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |    2     |     3     |    4     |
| Pet         | ferret | rat | lizard     | rabbit |
| Transport   | helicopter     | scooter    | van | jet-ski    |

