.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-6-5::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: water, tea, almond-milk, soy-milk
The people use 4 different means of transport: skateboard, quad-bike, motorbike, tram
1. the person drinking water is on the left of the person drinking soy-milk##1
2. the person drinking soy-milk is somewhere to the left of the person driving the motorbike##5
3. the person drinking soy-milk is somewhere to the left of the person driving the quad-bike##5
4. the person drinking tea is not the person driving the tram##6
5. the person driving the skateboard is not the person drinking water##6
6. the person drinking almond-milk is on the left of the person drinking tea##1
7. the person driving the motorbike is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |  2   |    3     |   4   |
| Beverage    | water        | soy-milk | almond-milk | tea |
| Transport   | tram | skateboard | quad-bike     | motorbike   |

