.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-6-6::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: zombie, time-travel, musical, animation
There are 4 different nationalities: turkish, malaysian, japanese, argentine
1. the turkish is on the right of the person watching zombie movies##1
2. the person watching animation movies is not the malaysian##6
3. the turkish is on the far right##1
4. the malaysian is somewhere to the right of the argentine##5
5. the person watching musical movies is the person watching musical movies##1
6. the person watching musical movies is somewhere to the left of the turkish##5
7. the person watching musical movies is somewhere to the left of the person watching zombie movies##5
8. the person watching time-travel movies is somewhere to the left of the argentine##5
9. the person watching time-travel movies is somewhere to the left of the argentine##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |   2    |     3     |     4      |
| Movie-Genre   | time-travel | musical    | zombie  | animation   |
| Nationality   | japanese  | argentine | malaysian | turkish |

