.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-6-7::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: satire, animation, adventure, martial-arts
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: blues, funk, salsa, disco
1. the fan salsa is on the left or right of the fan blues##3
2. the fan salsa is not the person watching animation movies##6
3. the person watching satire movies is the fan funk##1
4. the fan blues is on the left or right of the fan disco##3
5. the fan salsa is on the far left##1
6. the person watching animation movies is the fan blues##1
7. the person watching martial-arts movies is somewhere to the left of the fan blues##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2    |      3      |      4      |
| Movie-Genre   | martial-arts | animation     | adventure | satire |
| Music-Genre   | salsa | blues | disco      | funk         |

