3. the videographer is on the right of the dancer##1
4. the dancer is on the left or right of the person drinking hot-chocolate##3
5. the person drinking lemonade is on the left or right of the dancer##3
6. the doctor is on the left or right of the person drinking juice##3
7. the person drinking coffee is somewhere to the right of the person drinking lemonade##5
8. the person drinking hot-chocolate is not the videographer##6

.:: Answer ::.
|            |   1   |     2      |       3       |      4       |
| Beverage   | hot-chocolate  | juice        | lemonade      | coffee          |
| Job        | doctor | dancer | videographer | librarian |

