.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-6-9::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  police-officer, social-worker, nurse, designer
The people use 4 different means of transport: scooter, bike, bus, roller
1. the police-officer is in an odd position##4
2. the person driving the bike is not the designer##6
3. the person driving the scooter is somewhere to the right of the nurse##5
4. the person driving the roller is in an even position##4
5. the person driving the roller is on the left of the person driving the bus##1
6. the person driving the roller is the nurse##1
7. the police-officer is not the person driving the roller##6
8. the social-worker is somewhere to the right of the designer##5

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |   2    |     3      |     4     |
| Job         | police-officer  | nurse | designer    | social-worker |
| Transport   | bike | roller | bus | scooter  |

