.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-6-10::.
4 different pets are kept: dog, snake, horse, bird
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: skiing, lacrosse, basketball, parkour
1. the person who's sport is skiing is not the owner of the dog##6
2. the owner of the bird is on the left of the owner of the snake##1
3. the person who's sport is parkour is the person who's sport is parkour##1
4. the owner of the bird is on the right of the person who's sport is parkour##1
5. the owner of the horse is not the person who's sport is parkour##6
6. the person who's sport is lacrosse is not the owner of the snake##6
7. the person who's sport is parkour is in an even position##4
8. the owner of the horse is the person who's sport is skiing##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1     |       2       |    3    |    4     |
| Pet     | horse | dog        | bird  | snake     |
| Sport   | skiing     | parkour | lacrosse | basketball |

