.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-6-11::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: woodworking, singing, cooking, writing
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: soul, funk, techno, d&b
1. the person who's hobby is woodworking is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is writing##3
2. the fan funk is somewhere to the left of the person who's hobby is woodworking##5
3. the fan techno is not the person who's hobby is cooking##6
4. the person who's hobby is singing is between the fan d&b and the person who's hobby is cooking##2
5. the person who's hobby is cooking is on the left of the person who's hobby is singing##1
6. the fan funk is between the fan soul and the person who's hobby is woodworking##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |     2      |   3   |     4     |
| Hobby         | cooking | singing    | woodworking | writing |
| Music-Genre   | soul         | funk | d&b   | techno     |

