.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-6-12::.
There 4 different types of food: artichoke, raspberry, peach, pomegranate
The people use 4 different means of transport: skateboard, car, quad-bike, taxi
1. the person eating peach is somewhere to the right of the person driving the quad-bike##5
2. the person eating pomegranate is not the person driving the skateboard##6
3. the person driving the car is the person eating pomegranate##1
4. the person driving the car is on the right of the person eating raspberry##1
5. the person driving the quad-bike is not the person eating pomegranate##6
6. the person eating raspberry is not the person driving the skateboard##6
7. the person eating peach is somewhere to the left of the person eating raspberry##5
8. the person eating artichoke is on the left of the person eating peach##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |    2     |     3     |   4    |
| Food        | artichoke  | peach | raspberry | pomegranate |
| Transport   | quad-bike | skateboard     | taxi     | car    |

