4. the person eating orange is somewhere to the right of the person watching scientific movies##5
5. the person eating blueberry is between the person eating peas and the person watching family movies##2
6. the person eating peas is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |      2      |     3     |     4     |
