5. the person who's sport is basketball is between the photographer and the person who's sport is skiing##2
6. the photographer is not the person who's sport is surfing##6
7. the nurse is on the right of the firefighter##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1     |    2     |     3     |     4      |
