.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-6-19::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: card-games, sudoku, rock-climbing, writing
4 different pets are kept: guinea-pig, ferret, hedgehog, rat
1. the owner of the ferret is somewhere to the right of the owner of the hedgehog##5
2. the owner of the guinea-pig is somewhere to the right of the owner of the ferret##5
3. the owner of the ferret is on the left of the owner of the guinea-pig##1
4. the owner of the rat is not the person who's hobby is card-games##6
5. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is between the person who's hobby is card-games and the person who's hobby is sudoku##2
6. the person who's hobby is writing is on the far left or far right##3
7. the person who's hobby is writing is on the right of the person who's hobby is card-games##1
8. the owner of the rat is somewhere to the right of the owner of the ferret##5

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1    |     2     |      3      |      4      |
| Hobby   | sudoku | rock-climbing | card-games | writing |
| Pet     | hedgehog  | ferret      | guinea-pig  | rat       |

