The people use 4 different means of transport: bike, airplane, jet-ski, helicopter
1. the person driving the helicopter is on the left or right of the person drinking 7up##3
2. the person drinking fanta is on the left or right of the person driving the airplane##3
3. the person driving the bike is on the right of the person driving the jet-ski##1
4. the person driving the bike is not the person drinking sprite##6
5. the person drinking fanta is somewhere to the right of the person driving the airplane##5
6. the person driving the airplane is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|             |      1      |    2     |     3      |     4     |
| Beverage    | sprite | 7up | fanta      | juice   |
| Transport   | helicopter  | airplane   | jet-ski | bike |

 